data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bed/ 1 bath home that offers ample space. This residence provides a warm and inviting atmosphere for you & your family. As you approach the home, you will drive up to a well-maintained landscaping and the inviting curb appeal with fully electrical fenced in front yard Upon entering the front door, you'll find yourself in the spacious living room. This space is perfect for hosting guests or enjoying quality family time. The home has large backyard with ample space for a pool and another bathroom addition.
